# Django Messages DRF
---

`django-messages-drf` is an alternative of `pinax-messages` using django rest framework.

Supported Django and Python Versions
------------------------------------

+-----------------+-----+-----+-----+
| Django / Python | 3.6 | 3.7 | 3.8 |
+=================+=====+=====+=====+
|  2.2            |  *  |  *  |  *  |
+-----------------+-----+-----+-----+
|  3.0            |  *  |  *  |  *  |
+-----------------+-----+-----+-----+
|  3.1            |  *  |  *  |  *  |
+-----------------+-----+-----+-----+


